Geographic Codes 2.0.0

	* Better logic for internal/private IP addresses on geolookup widgets.
	* NEW GEO FEATURES!
	* Migrate i18n logic from .ini to .yml.
	-- Charlie Powell <charlie@evalagency.com>  Wed, 20 Jul 2016 02:11:16 -0400

Geographic Codes 1.7.0

	* [Performance] Better performance on IP lookups and added country methods for retrieving the flag and
	  country name from a result.
	* Copyright update from 2015 to 2016.
	* Display the country name as the title text instead of the ISO-2 code.
	* Better support for caching IP lookups that result in an error, (albiet with a much shorter cache
	  TTL).
	* Compiler
	* Switch to Core's built-in country flag assets.
	* Remove geocode\Country as it duplicates GeoCountryModel and the model is better at it.
	* New view, geoaddress/lookupip for performing IP lookups against the geo database directly.
	* Remove the large version of country flags from geographic-codes as Core now has smaller versions
	  embedded.
	* Ensure that GeoAddressModel is compatible with Core 5.0 models.
	* Decrease the size of the keys for GeoAddressModel so the total keysize is < 1000 bytes.
	* Add an index for the new model/record_key to speed up lookups based on those criteria.
	* Add support for GeoAddress models to have the linking parent inline.
	-- Charlie Powell <charlie@evalagency.com>  Wed, 23 Mar 2016 22:23:42 -0400

